).

Labral formula of chaetae: 4/1,4,2 (
Fig. 4
). Maxillary palp simple with one basal chaeta and two sublobal hairs. Labial palp of 
type
AC, papillae A to E with 1, 4, 0, 3 and 2 guard chaetae respectively (
