Dorsal pso formula as 32/133/33343, and ventral as 11/000/01110 (
Figs 1 & 7
). Subcoxa 1 of legs I, II and III with 2, 2 and 2 pso respectively. Parapseudocelli only visible on Abd. I sternum at the base of VT as 1+1. Pseudopore formula: 00/011/11110 dorsally and 00/111/0001m0 ventrally (
Figs 1 & 7
