Ordinary chaetae differentiated in micro-, meso- and macrochaetae. S-chaetae weakly thickened but distinguishable from ordinary chaetae, S-chaetae formula: 11/011/222121 dorsally and 11/000/000100 ventrally (
Figs 1 & 7
